          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Copyright and Trademarks</h2>
          <h3>Website Content</h3>
          <p>
            All content on this website, including but not limited to text, graphics, logos, button icons, images, audio clips, digital downloads, data compilations, and software, is the property of Stardew Valley Guide or its content suppliers and is protected by international copyright laws.
          </p>

